    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small dings, and some fading on the clear coat in certain spots. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few minor stains, though it remains functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it has high mileage and will likely require some routine maintenance or minor repairs in the near future to keep it in peak operating shape. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for a budget-friendly option that still has life left in it.",
      "price": 21500.0,
