    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sophisticated design. This unit has been maintained to rigorous standards, ensuring a seamless driving experience for its next proprietor. Featuring a refined interior and a robust powertrain, it offers an exceptional balance of performance and long-term reliability. We invite discerning buyers to inspect this well-preserved example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
