    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a gem. It\u2019s in great shape, runs smoothly, and has been really well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out for a weekend getaway, this beauty is ready to hit the road. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.1-generation Carrera is a purist-spec driver, powered by the M96/05 3.6L flat-six engine. The powertrain features a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle that delivers power to the rear wheels with the mechanical immediacy only a naturally aspirated boxer can provide. To ensure long-term durability, the IMS bearing has been proactively upgraded with a ceramic solution, and the rear main seal (RMS) was replaced simultaneously. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, utilizing its original MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry to provide surgical turn-in and high-speed composure. Braking performance is anchored by four-piston monoblock calipers and vented, cross-drilled rotors, offering excellent thermal management and pedal feel. This is a mechanically sorted example with a clean underside and a healthy torque curve, ideal for the owner who prioritizes driving dynamics and engineering integrity.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Mechanically sound. Minor cosmetic wear. Clean interior. Regular maintenance performed. Service records available.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride of ownership, offering a harmonious blend of reliability and sophisticated style. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous gloss that catches the light beautifully, showing only the minor, expected character marks of careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of cleanliness; the upholstery is supple and free of tears, while the dashboard and console remain vibrant and crack-free. Every electronic feature, from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having followed a strict maintenance regimen that results in a smooth, quiet idle and responsive acceleration. The steering is tight, and the braking is firm and confident. This is a well-sorted, turn-key vehicle perfect for someone who values a car that has been respected and preserved.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic refinement. This specimen offers dependable performance coupled with a well-preserved interior, ensuring a premium driving experience. Rigorously inspected to meet our professional standards, it stands as a testament to consistent care and quality engineering. An exceptional acquisition for the discerning driver seeking both value and reliability.",
      "price": 34850.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
