      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes the preferred Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering power to the rear wheels via a factory 3.62:1 limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes rear subframe reinforcement and a full cooling system overhaul. The chassis retains its signature torsional rigidity, complemented by refreshed bushings and a precise steering rack. A driver-focused machine with linear power delivery and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline, this M3 is optimized for both spirited canyon runs and technical circuit use.",
